Package: dremeR
Type: Package
Title: An R Interface to the MEME Suite
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: Spencer Nystrom <snystrom@email.unc.edu> [aut, cre]
Description: Provides functions for performing motif analysis in R using the MEME suite as a backend.
    Functions & outputs are designed for easy integration into tidy workflows for rapid iteration and delayed evaluation using futures if desired.
